Package fr.upmc.dtgui.annotations

Enum Summary
VariationType  
 

Annotation Types Summary
BooleanActuatorData The annotation BooleanActuatorData tags setter methods of a robot with information concerning how to use the corresponding boolean data in the robot representation as a control over the robot's behavior.
BooleanSensorData The annotation RealSensorData tags getter methods of a robot with information concerning how to use the corresponding boolean data in the robot representation as a property that can be observed to look into the robot's state.
IntegerActuatorData The annotation IntegerActuatorData tags setter methods of a robot with information concerning how to use the corresponding integer data in the robot representation as a control over the robot's behavior.
IntegerRange The annotation IntegerRange is used in an annotation IntegerSensorData ou IntegerActuatorData to define the range of admissible values for the corresponding data.
IntegerSensorData The annotation RealSensorData tags getter methods of a robot with information concerning how to use the corresponding integer data in the robot representation as a property that can be observed to look into the robot's state.
MeasurementUnit  
RealActuatorData The annotation RealActuatorData tags setter methods of a robot with information concerning how to use the corresponding real data in the robot representation as a control over the robot's behavior.
RealRange The annotation RealRange is used in an annotation RealSensorData ou RealActuatorData to define the range of admissible values for the corresponding data.
RealSensorData The annotation RealSensorData tags getter methods of a robot with information concerning how to use the corresponding real data in the robot representation as a property that can be observed to look into the robot's state.
WithActuators The annotation WithActuators indicates that the annotated class has actuators and uses actuator annotations to define these.
WithSensors The annotation WithSensors indicates that the annotated class has sensory data and uses sensor annotations to define these.
